{
  "stem": "58.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you ever hear of what the word means, Umschlagplatz?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK-- the Umschlagplatz was the place where they shipped all the Jews out, either to Auschwitz, or to Germany, mostly to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, trains-- a train depot-- right across.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I looked up from the factory, the window, you could see the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, if you interview more people, maybe they'll mention this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they made us-- us-- well, at first when they brought us in from the farm, and they placed us in those buildings, there was a small pick-up, a few hundred people, they needed-- every day they needed to fill up the trains.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But those people from the kibbutz weren't going easily, they fought back right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were already organized with some weapons, and they fought back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those two sisters that I mentioned, when they saw me at the farm first, they picked them up and sent them to a-- to a camp somewhere.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we were still working, and we were watching through the windows, how they pick people up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As long as we were at the factory, we were safe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, a guy-- I sit in my-- we had only one room, we got in-- in one bed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to sleep across the bed, my two sisters and I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if we had nothing to do, my aunt and uncle had a big apartment, so we went to sit there before we went to sleep, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this, about three, four people from the underground comes in to my-- they ring the bell, come into my uncle's place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say you, is you Israel Gromon?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, Israel Gromon.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I see the one going from the kibbutz, Feifke, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
